data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Choose LEVITATING WOMAN before you plunge. Plunge when START ILLUSION is available in display. Hit the trunk and shoot the middle ramp until you get bored. You really don't have to do anything else. Keep that combo going!
When you are really bored lock 2 balls and go for multiball. Make sure you get max bonus multiplier.
When you are back to normal play you can shoot the trunk a few times to lit a new mode but don't start it! Keep hammering that middle ramp until drain.
Ball 2:
If you are lucky 2X COMBO might be available as skill shot. Be sure not to miss that. 2X COMBO makes the combos count twice as fast making it much easier scoring huge combo points.
You can get 1B in 2 minutes using this strategy on ball 1.
